      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNIGHT MOTH (4) kicked off his career with a win as a hot favourite two-and-a-half weeks ago, racing parked before getting home by 2 metres at Geelong. Hails from a top yard and should only be better for the experience so can work through his grades. SAVON DE ROCHE (9) added to a string of wins and placings when when scoring by 4.6m at her latest appearance, taking her record here to four from seven. Came from this row to miss by a head prior. Go well again. LETS WENT (3) is first up for four-and-a-half months but he is a three-time fresh winner so expect a good effort to kick off this prep. ANIMADO (5) has claims off a Melton win from the back line three back.",
